dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.transportprotocols

Interface IFlexrayTpConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable, ITpConfig

    public interface IFlexrayTpConfig
extends IEntity, ITpConfig
    IFlexrayTpConfig: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This element defines exactly one FlexRay ISO TP Configuration. One FlexRayTpConfig element shall be created for each FlexRay Network in the System that uses FlexRay Iso Tp.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
